headline: Microchip Technology (MCHP) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: Microchip Tech (MCHP) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 10% and 0.98%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
